long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A basic tab manager that allows you to find or navigate to tabs quickly, as well as pin or unpin tabs, and mute or unmute audible tabs.

v0.1.2 includes case-insensitive tab searching by title.
v0.3.3 includes the ability to close tabs, the ability to pin and unpin tabs, and an updated shortcut key (Ctrl+Shift+E) that should have fewer conflicts with other extensions.
v0.3.4 includes the ability to show audible and muted tabs, and mute or unmute audible tabs.
